@10 = ~Le Faiseur de nuit +3
Owned by a Dragon Highlord, Verminaard, Nightbringer is a footman's Masse and a powerful tool of evil. Created by the Prêtres of the Queen of Darkness, Nightbringer causes any victim struck by the Masse to go blind.
Nightbringer may only be used by those of inherent evil.   
